{"tid":471791,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實莊子死左關動物台咩事","createTime":"2017-11-17T14:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T14:31:33.000Z","uid":150609,"like":3,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"09dc22b236ffcb47365c61ef6015b2681e0cc434","tid":471791,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/225524_c112c5510b45371ce059019bbb9bbfa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F225524_c112c5510b45371ce059019bbb9bbfa7.jpg&h=54b9f418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莊子（約前369年&mdash;前286年）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時d死毒撚又話叫人唔好講 卡通 動漫<br />\n<br />\n而家又用埋d on9翻譯名<br />\n<br />\n莊乜野子  Buruma點解可以叫做莊子<br />\n<br />\n你話佢抄西遊記 咁你叫佢唐三藏囉  關莊子咩事<br />\n<br />\nd老屎忽因為不嬲用開垃圾譯名  用左幾十年 就變左正確名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b165ebee83909c7650874bf1dad315ad403090","tid":471791,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe9effbd494d64e0a8bda3e5b3e7eecd7f72b33","tid":471791,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n......<br />\n......<br />\nha..."},{"pid":"ba2164c9d025468572b63e4a607bfe6516423269","tid":471791,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>...<br />\n......<br />\n......<br />\nha...</blockquote><br />\n好...<br />\n尷...<br />\n尬..."},{"pid":"7961af38a504679ab098762315fc7da7e2b5cbe9","tid":471791,"uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"d毒撚諗唔到點駁  唯一可以用到既 <br />\n<br />\n只有留低個負皮 死死氣咁出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446d3e4b7062fe4f878433ed2f951a0951b4da90","tid":4