mal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 李阿寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 葉大雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5bd825ea1d9639173deeec1f4e0790943b527","tid":471791,"uid":84032,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote> 乜人識個奘字, 就變左莊子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有人回唔洗玩單機版<br />\n<br />\n即<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">系</span></span>用5P字  即<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">系</span></span>低質譯名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都係單機啦 Blocked"}]}